Name: Final Fantasy XI Online: Seekers of Adoulin
Overview:
Seekers of Adoulin is the fifth expansion for Final Fantasy XI Online.

It offers a variety of new features, such as monsters, areas in the lands of Ulbuka, and two additional jobs: Geomancer and Rune Seeker. It was released as a digital download for Windows. Only the Xbox360 version is available as physical media in North-America and Europe, but Japan has a physical release for PS2 as well.

It requires Final Fantasy XI Online and PlayOnline.
